<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <style>
    /* Styling for the main section */
    main {
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #23086f;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Small heading with dark red color */
    .highlight-title {
      font-size: 2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #d84315;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    /* Instructor image section */
    .instructor-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .instructor-section h3 {
      color: #d84315;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Set instructor image width to 80% of original */
    .instructor-image {
      width: 80%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    /* Navbar link text color to white */
    header nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<header style="background-color: #444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
  <h1><%= title %></h1>
  <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="highlight-title">Bushido Martial Art</div>
  <h2>Discover Strength, Discipline, and Community</h2>
  <p>
    Welcome to Bushido Martial Arts School. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced fighter, 
    we have something for everyone. Join us to learn, grow, and challenge yourself.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our programs are designed for both children and adults, helping students build confidence, improve health, and develop discipline. 
    Through structured training, students gain physical strength and mental resilience while learning the true spirit of martial arts.
  </p>
  <p>
    The school is led by our Head Instructor, a highly experienced martial artist with over 30 years of training and teaching. 
    He holds a black belt in five martial arts — Karate, Japanese Jiujitsu, Shorinji Kempo, Hapkido (Korean Federation), and World Martial Arts Hapkido — 
    as well as a brown belt in Judo. With deep knowledge and passion, he is committed to guiding each student on their martial arts journey.
  </p>

  <!-- Instructor Image Section -->
  <div class="instructor-section">
    <h3>Instructor</h3>
    <img src="/images/instructor.jpeg" alt="Instructor Photo" class="instructor-image" />
  </div>
</main>

<footer style="background-color: #444; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 15px;">
  <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Bushido Martial Arts School</p>
  <p>
    Sunnynook Community Center, Sunnynook, Forrest Hill, Auckland<br>
    Phone: 021 579 574<br>
    Email: <a href="mailto:ari1701@yahoo.com" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">ari1701@yahoo.com</a>
  </p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>